        [
          "title",
          "The Dock"
        ],
        [
          "exit",
          "north"
        ],
        [
          "exit",
          "east"
        ]
      ],
      "content": "Weathered planks creak beneath your feet as the dock juts out over grey-green water. Fishing boats knock gently against their moorings, their paint flaking in long pale strips. The smell of salt and tar hangs in the still air. A cobbled road leads north toward the village, and a sandy path follows the shoreline east."
    },
    {
      "kind": 30078,
      "tags": [
        [
          "d",
          "tides-end-01-basics:place:village-square"
        ],
        [
          "t",
