        [
          "title",
          "Village Square"
        ],
        [
          "exit",
          "south"
        ],
        [
          "exit",
          "east"
        ],
        [
          "exit",
          "west"
        ]
      ],
      "content": "A modest square of packed earth ringed by low stone buildings with slate roofs. A dry fountain stands in the centre, its basin cracked and filled with windblown leaves. Smoke drifts from a chimney to the east where a tavern sign swings on rusted chains. To the west, a gap between the houses opens onto dunes and the sound of surf."
    },
    {
      "kind": 30078,
      "tags": [
        [
          "d",
          "tides-end-01-basics:place:the-tavern"
        ],
        [
          "t",
          "tides-end-01-basics"
        ],
        [
          "type",
          "place"
        ],
        [
          "title",
          "The Tavern"
        ],
        [
          "exit",
          "west"
        ]
      ],
      "content": "The low-ceilinged room is warm and dim, lit by tallow candles guttering in glass jars. A long bar of driftwood planks runs along the far wall, its surface stained dark with years of spilled ale. Empty stools line the bar and a few rough tables fill the room. The only way out is west, back to the square."
    },
    {
