        ],
        [
          "exit",
          "west"
        ]
      ],
      "content": "Coarse sand stretches in a long curve between dark rocks and the restless sea. Kelp and driftwood lie in tangled lines where the last high tide left them. Gulls wheel overhead, their cries thin against the wind. The village lies east through a gap in the dunes, and a rocky coastal path leads west toward the dock."
